{"tid":1694057,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"華盛頓郵報：現在已經是一場戰爭，香港，為自由而戰。","createTime":"2019-11-05T02:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T05:11:16.000Z","uid":54564,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d3ca5189d2507866314f39d8031090e89df177","tid":1694057,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:46:46.000Z","msg":"Opinion | 'It is a war here now.' Inside Hong Kong's fight for freedom.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I7pxzy4rwb8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DI7pxzy4rwb8&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwBx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=0b953e26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I7pxzy4rwb8</a><br />\n<br />\nWhat began as a series of peaceful protests against a proposed law to allow the Hong Kong government to extradite residents to mainland China has become a de facto war about the future of democracy. After nearly six months of resistance, who are the Hong Kongers keeping this seemingly impossible fight alive? Producer Parjanya Christian Holtz follows a teacher, a student and a tech worker who have sacrificed thousands of hours &mdash; and dollars &mdash; for the movement.<br />\n<br />\n將近六個月嘅鬥爭，香港人一步一步咁進步緊，香港成為咗2019年嘅年度主角<br />\n就算再失望，再絕望，都唔可以放棄<br />\n如果唔係，我哋對唔住為我哋付出生命、前途嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n香港人，應承我，繼續一齊走落去<br />\n\b&quot;There is no real leader commanding us or giving us instruction on what to do, we do whatever we believe what's right.&quot;  -- (Chong, 2019)<br />\n<br />\n雖然近日好多手足被捕，就連和理非唱歌嗌口號都被打壓，<br />\n好多人都唔知可以做d乜嘢好，不斷喺度淨好嬲好嬲<br />\n但，只要我哋一日唔放棄，呢場戰爭一日都未完<br />\n<br />\n我代表唔到大家，但我相信大家都會keep住做自己認為正確嘅事<br />\n直至成功或者戰死至一兵一卒為止，我會一路為香港而戰，因為呢度喺我哋嘅屋企<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"8ea0b97e77d769f0aac99da2c695faad38597a46","tid":1694057,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7403cf9dfa1f3d358993d18f142d3b7ae6e805be","tid":1694057,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6374882c75b8b8595bd32c75620cf3adead2fc08","tid":1694057,"uid":54564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"雖然近排失敗主義風吹得幾勁<br />\n但我相信真。香港人，失望完之後只會更繼續努力去為香港而戰"},{"pid":"9402829e37ceaabb8d0b94ec0b6bf03d1cecd8ab","tid":1694057,"uid":181549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:53:45.000Z","msg":"只要仲有一口氣 我都會繼續出黎抗爭<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"1651e57ca1305657076044071208de9344eee941","tid":1694057,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6374882c75b8b8595bd32c75620cf3adead2fc08","tid":1694057,"uid":54564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"雖然近排失敗主義風吹得幾勁<br />\n但我相信真。香港人，失望完之後只會更繼續努力去為香港而戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"你知唔失敗撚只可以係連登生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登點唔代表出面點嫁<br />\n最要係見到班失敗撚即刻拉post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160260b4207e55ed1b290a401ec3360089506689","tid":1694057,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1651e57ca1305657076044071208de9344eee941","tid":1694057,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6374882c75b8b8595bd32c75620cf3adead2fc08","tid":1694057,"uid":54564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"雖然近排失敗主義風吹得幾勁<br />\n但我相信真。香港人，失望完之後只會更繼續努力去為香港而戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"你知唔失敗撚只可以係連登生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登點唔代表出面點嫁<br />\n最要係見到班失敗撚即刻拉post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:07:16.000Z","msg":"真 永遠出到去現場 <br />\n<br />\n從來未見過有人會話放火拆鋪暴力，冇人會怨冇車搭返屋企<br />\n只會有師奶叔叔伯伯係咁叫手足小心，然後拍曬手讚大家做得好<br />\n